overview:
&lt;p&gt;This villa is a perfect vacation stay to unleash your eternal happiness and peace. A lavishing 7 bhk villa is available for stay at Candolim, with a landscape view of Mandovi river is an ideal choice for renting for your big family or friends group. The mind-numbing enormous villa will surely make your Goa trip memorable. The villa&amp;#39;s facade looks like nothing less than a five-star hotel. The villa has a jaw-dropping interior design. The villa is fully furnished with cozy and royal furniture. The villa&amp;#39;s enormous glass windows and doors will surely make your stay luxurious. The colossal balconies will surely turn your sky-gazing daydream true. Even there are special cozy sitting arrangements on the balconies. The villa&amp;#39;s mind-blowing interior design has a cafe aspire theme. Countless sofas and other fancy furniture are arranged in the hall. The immense lamps in the hall are specially hung for your late-night conversations along with your family and friends. The infinity pool merges with the river and the ocean. The decent color theme is applied by keeping in mind your peace. The retro posters and paintings enrich the indoor environment. The bedrooms are specially designed to make sure your complete relaxation by keeping them plan shades of white with minimal designed wooden furniture. The washrooms are thoroughly clean to maintain your hygiene. The massive mirrors, tiny and antique showpieces, and fresh indoor plants will add delight to your stay.&lt;/p&gt;

