&lt;p&gt;The rooms are well furnished with beautiful furniture with a wooden texture. All the rooms are fully air-conditioned and have luminous lights that fill brightness all around. The property has an enormous swimming pool that you can enjoy with your entire family and friends. The beautiful surroundings have plantations all around with beautiful scenery for you to adore. All the rooms in the apartments are very spacious and clean. You can enjoy cooking in our fully equipped kitchenette. The kitchen also has a refrigerator to store essential stuff. All the bedrooms are very cozy which makes you feel like home has kind-sized beds and soft cushions for you to relax after a very energetic day. The bathrooms have all the amenities with proper showers and western toilets. The balconies have beautiful furniture to sit and chill and have a cup of hot coffee or tea in your hand recollecting all your memories. The small patio beside the pool is where you can enjoy the landscape view. Having amazing nature all around you is what you want while staying and spending your lovely vacation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This property is located medially having restaurants and cafes nearby where you can visit or order your favorite food. Beaches are just 10 minutes of walk away from the property&amp;#39;s location. This is a perfect blend of luxury and comfort that fits your huge family or friends reunion.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;For the comfort and security check, please take time to note and read the House rules and Policies.&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Apt SB RF 028 is an amazing choice because of its:&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Grandiose allocation space for your entire family and friends group&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Location that is surrounded by lush green trees and plants allowing you to enjoy the nature&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Swimming pool where you can swim to splash all your worries away&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Nearby access to the Baga and Calangute beaches which are 10 minute walk from the property&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;spacious rooms and a well-equipped kitchen for you to cook whenever you want&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;For us, your comfort comes first! For that, we add these amenities:&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;All time security for our guests&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;High-speed WIFI connection&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A Genset for power cut issues&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Property manager for any issues&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Caretaker for taking care of your needs&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Housekeeping once a day&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Evening turndown services are available&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;There is 24 hours water supply and Free Wi-Fi&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Electric Kettle is available&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Toaster, Induction, and other essential appliances provided&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Washing machine for cleaning clothes&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Iron/Ironing Board are provided&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;SERVICES AT AN EXTRA COST&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Chef for lunch and dinner&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Car/bike rentals at an extra cost&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Airport transfers at an extra cost&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Restaurant suggestions&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sightseeing tours at an extra cost&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;The spacious room tour:&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;2 BHK APARTMENT&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The Apartment is on the ground floor, first floor, and second floor&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;There are 2 bedrooms with wide windows allowing bright sunlight to fill the room&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Rooms are organized and have AC in each room&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;King-sized beds with cushions and blankets provided&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;High-speed Wi-Fi and TV connection is provided in each room&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;There are 2 bathrooms that are beautifully tiled and have a shower and a western toilet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;KITCHEN&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Guests have the access to the kitchen&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Simple food, tea, coffee, and instant noodles can be made&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Crockery and cutlery are ready to use when needed&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It has a microwave, gas stove, refrigerator; and other essential things&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;FOOD&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Cook for breakfast is available from 8 am to 11 am&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Ingredients and groceries will be charged as per actuals&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Cook charges for lunch, and dinner will be charged as per individuals&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Guests can order food from nearby restaurants if needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;AVAILABILITY OF MANAGER/CARETAKER&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The caretaker of the villa will be available&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;He will be present at the villa if anything is needed for your comfort&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The manager will communicate via calls or messages anytime if needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;FUN ACTIVITIES&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A vacation comes with lots of fun and games. Collect memories while playing with your kids, family, or friends. It can be both indoor and outdoor games. The property gives you a lot of space to enjoy playing in the courtyard or gazing at the stars or having a lovely conversation with your loved ones. The massive living room is where you can sit with your group and play various games and create loads of memories. Swimming in the pool and playing various pool games is what you can do for fun. You can have a walk on the beach enjoying the sunrise and sunset.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;NEARBY TRAVEL ROUTES/ TRANSPORTATION&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Distance from Goa International Airport: 41 km&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Thivim Railway Station: 17 km&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Mapusa Bus Terminal: 7.2 km&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Panjim Bus Stand: 16 km&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;WHAT&amp;#39;S AROUND&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Goa is an absolute choice for spending your vacation and making loads of memories. People from all over the world visit Goa every year making it a famous location. People experience the Portuguese culture and Goan heritage on this beautiful land. Not only the adorable landscape and scenic beaches but also the colorful Goan houses are the prime attraction here. This is a paradise for party lovers, people have a blast on new year&amp;#39;s eve every year. A bag full of memories you pack with yourself back to your pavilion.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Enjoy paragliding at famous locations&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Live an adventurous life doing various water sports like kayaking, jet skiing, and many more&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Explore the astonishing corals and marine life diving deep into the sea&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Bike rides are a must to explore and wander around the villages in Goa&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

