&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The full payment must be made for your booking to be confirmed.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Security is to be paid before check-in.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In case there is a lockdown in the Goa / City Of Origin, we can refund the full advance payment.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Foreign nationals have to share their passport and visa details before their stay.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;To avail of this, you need to send aadhar card copies for all guests.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The number of guests must not exceed the count previously mentioned at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Any harm to the property will be charged as per the actual repairing amount or replacement amount.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Only guests registered are allowed on the premises of the villa.&lt;/li&gt;
